options.query:
WITH RECURSIVE Navigation AS (
  SELECT
    p.id AS id,
    p.name,
    p.sort,
    p.show,
    p.resolveSlug,
    pl.Lang,
    pl.label,
    l.code AS langCode,
    IFNULL(r.name, 'all') AS access,
    ('/' || l.code) AS path,
    ('/' || l.code) AS sortedPath
  FROM HcPages AS p
    JOIN HcPagesLang AS pl ON pl.Page = p.id
    JOIN HcLangs AS l ON l.id = pl.Lang
    LEFT JOIN HcRoles AS r ON r.id = p.Role
  WHERE p.Parent = '' AND l.active = TRUE
  UNION
  SELECT
    p.id AS id,
    p.name,
    p.sort,
    p.show,
    p.resolveSlug,
    pl.Lang,
    pl.label,
    l.code AS langCode,
    IFNULL(r.name, 'all') AS access,
    (n.path || '/' || pl.slug) AS path,
    (n.path || '/' || (p.sort + 1) || '.' || pl.slug) AS sortedPath
  FROM HcPages AS p
	JOIN Navigation AS n ON p.Parent = n.id
    JOIN HcPagesLang As pl ON pl.Page = p.id
    JOIN HcLangs As l ON l.id = pl.Lang
    LEFT JOIN HcRoles As r ON r.id = p.Role
  WHERE pl.Lang = n.Lang
)
SELECT id, name, sort, show, resolveSlug, Lang AS lang, langCode, path, sortedPath FROM Navigation ORDER BY Lang, path;
